$E = \frac{(6.626 \times 10^{-34} \mathrm{~J~s}) \times (3.00 \times 10^8 \mathrm{~m/s})}{300 \times 10^{-9} \mathrm{~m}} = \frac{19.878 \times 10^{-26} \mathrm{~J~m}}{300 \times 10^{-9} \mathrm{~m}} = 6.626 \times 10^{-19} \mathrm{~J}$.

