Since 17% have an irregular heartbeat, and we've found that 5.95% have irregular heartbeat and high blood pressure, and 7.15% have irregular heartbeat and normal blood pressure, the percentage with irregular heartbeat and low blood pressure is 17% - (5.95% + 7.15%) = 17% - 13.1% = 3.9%.

