To find the percentage of patients with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure, we first note that 19% have low blood pressure. The percentage with irregular heartbeat and low blood pressure is 3.9%. Thus, the percentage with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure is 19% - 3.9% = 15.1%.

